page.title: 19RELIGION
page.content: There are a group of people called the{JESUS FELLOWSHIP}which is the main following in KISLINGBURY.This is a group which put most of their money towards their group. The main church in KISLINGBURY is called{St.Lukes Church}. Over the years it has had forty vicars. One of the best known ones was {ARCHIBALD {GRAHEM C.B.E.}who was assistant bishop of Peterborough around the time of 1965. The church originally had a tower,but it collapsed. They rebuilt it with a spire on top. Also in KISLINGBURY there is a { {BAPTIST CHURCH}. In Harpole there is also a {BAPTIST {CHURCH}and a{CHURCH OF ENGLAND . The Church of England was built in 1200.It has a tower and a graveyard.
